Version History

v1.0.0 (Initial Release)
- Add web browser sidebar to Anki editor
- Support for multiple tabs
- Navigation controls (back, forward, reload)
- URL bar with Google search fallback
- Keyboard shortcuts:
  * Ctrl+Shift+L: Toggle browser
  * Ctrl+T: New tab
  * Ctrl+W: Close tab
  * Ctrl+L: Focus URL bar
  * Ctrl+R: Reload page
  * Ctrl+[: Back
  * Ctrl+]: Forward
- Persistent cookies for maintaining login sessions
- JavaScript enabled by default
- Configurable start URL through settings dialog
- Modern tab-based interface with:
  * Closable tabs
  * Movable tabs
  * Tab title elision for long titles
  * Tab persistence between sessions
